Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的呢 跟渚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 无法查明原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 估计会像渚小姐一样今后也一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都还那么健康的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的父亲是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就要拿出个做父亲的样子来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 你不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人偶的我感觉不到寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的手一定变得很冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我连这一点也感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快世界就要变得一片雪白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我会一直在你身边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔或许会跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个最后一棒都休息的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计很难能找到人代替的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 要战胜阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要待在你身边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是站在我这边的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是站在你这边的 不管发生什么都会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我哪儿也不会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期 两星期
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一个月过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐的烧仍然没有退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说是去幼儿园 就连房门都出不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我来讲 实在不想让冈崎君就这么辞职了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看来你也有很多苦衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很果断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨跟大叔劝过我 但我想待在汐身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有积蓄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点 因为有在存她的学费
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上吧 别弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.52,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手柄上刻的是「芳野」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 明天开始的工作会很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换把你的螺丝刀借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你回来了就还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等小汐好点了就回来吧 在那之前就借我用用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会爱惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐一直在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有考虑过住院 但最后还是没有去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有治疗方法的话 就算去了也没有多大意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是 汐想要待在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣换一套新的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用起来哦 爸爸会帮你换的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉强 现在就算一个人做不到也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐已经不能一个人换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能一个人上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭也只能吃些不太硬的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平稳的日常生活 是不是不会再回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 有想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的话就说哦 不论是玩具还是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么我都会给你买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想跟爸爸一起去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事一点也不开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸脾气不好 还会大声吼叫什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心 还想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上电车 跟爸爸一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你病好了就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 不要为难爸爸好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己女儿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的一个愿望 我也不能帮她实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候如果有你在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是单纯地被这个小镇所玩弄着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻易地被赋予了幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又被轻易地夺去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要救汐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能收啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么固执
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我并不是固执
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有点积蓄 还能撑一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要敢骗我的话就修理你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人难做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但该守护的东西还是必须守护好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 真到不行的时候会跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我戒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是明智的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们牺牲了这片大自然建起了这所医院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来会牺牲什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇外的山丘已经开始被挖开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎要建个购物街
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会变得方便 所以对居民来说是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你把快要不行了的渚带到这里来的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚就和这座小镇连接在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后渚的女儿汐也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐被改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐被改变样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这座小镇来说是痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和痛苦没什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊 渐渐地在改变」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇只会这样觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人的死也只是被改变的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就不得不接受这个事实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为人们不愿接受 才建起了医院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿这座小镇和居民们 幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很凉 要慢慢喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气喝下去会闹肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等你病好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去那片花田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在去北方的话会很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去南方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既温暖又热闹的 空气新鲜的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等你病好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了好几次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 现在就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那片花田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要现在才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸两人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果不舒服了就要老老实实地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一个人走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了不要勉强的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和爸爸一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就一起走到你能走到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就快快乐乐地旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的不舒服的话一定要告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐喜欢雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 爸爸也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能走吗 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稍微休息一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁还没有下大前上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来背你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电车里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经在电车里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑 已经是晚上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 已经是深夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也最喜欢汐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救汐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来 谁来救救汐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要走多久才能到达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是已经近在眼前了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 仍旧遥不可及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这座小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里充满了想要忘却的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天去学校听听课 和朋友聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到根本不想回去的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 以后会有什么改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一样的生活会到来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆沙面包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这所学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 所有的这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在不断改变着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里和她搭话的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会和渚相遇 开始交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是不这样做比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这次的邂逅…
